    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Katon)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 8 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 23 | <b>Successes:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 11 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 25</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You focus Chakra around your body, forming an invisible shield that reacts to all incoming attacks, releasing a burst of flame to deflect or mitigate the damage.<br><br>You gain a +4 deflection bonus to Defense, DR 15/and a Fire and Cold resistance of 30. Any creature that hits with an unarmed or weapon attack and does not deal damage (due to your DR and resistances) suffers 1d4 fire damage per hit (CR applies).<br><br>The technique ends when an attack breaches the DR.</p>\n\n\n\n",
